        <header class="overview-header">
            <div class="overview-header__inner">
                <div class="overview-header__headline">
                    <h1 class="headline headline--1 f-w-semibold">Alumni Programmes</h1>
                </div>
                
                    <div class="overview-header__text">
                        <div class="text">
                            <p>Once a Humboldtian, always a Humboldtian. Even after the first research stay has come to an end, we still maintain close links to the alumni of our fellowship and award programmes. Our alumni sponsorship is tailored to the needs of every single Humboldtian, providing flexible support for your particular development and path in life as well as for cooperation with others. To achieve this, we offer you the following sponsorship opportunities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                
            </div>
        </header>
        <div class="overview__content">
            <div class="overview__inner">
                
		<section class="overview__section" id="c9974">
			
	
	
