                    <h3 class="headline headline--2 f-w-semibold teaser__headline">
                        Sponsorship for alumni abroad</h3>
                    
                        <div class="teaser__text">
                            <p>Even after your research stay in Germany, we offer the alumni of our fellowship and award programmes for researchers form abroad a raft of sponsorship opportunities. As a valued member of our growing network you will benefit from numerous advantages – during your entire lifetime.</p>
                        </div>
                    
                </div>
